msgstr "Standart Aeon Tajo fonini foydalanuvchi tanlagan boshqa fonga o'zgartiradi."

msgctxt "#31212"
msgid "Current background path: "
msgstr "Joriy fon yo'li:"

msgctxt "#31213"
msgid "Reset skin default background"
msgstr "Teri fonini asl holatiga qaytarish"

msgctxt "#31214"
msgid "Resets the default background provided with Aeon Tajo."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo bilan taqdim etilgan standart fonni tiklaydi."

msgctxt "#31215"
msgid "Show the coloured version of the icons rather than the monochrome version."
msgstr "Monoxrom versiyani emas, balki piktogrammalarning rangli versiyasini ko'rsating."

msgctxt "#31216"
msgid "Displays background and fanart images with a subtle motion effect across the screen."
msgstr "Ekran bo'ylab nozik harakat effekti bilan fon va fanart tasvirlarini ko'rsatadi."

msgctxt "#31217"
msgid "Displays a list in the video views featuring thumbnail images of the main actors from the movie or TV show's cast."
msgstr "Video ko‘rinishlarida film yoki teleko‘rsatuvdagi asosiy aktyorlarning eskiz tasvirlari aks etgan ro‘yxatni ko‘rsatadi."

msgctxt "#31218"
msgid "Search the Studio Icons add-on for logo images of the film studios of the movie/TV show, and if found, display them while browsing the video views."
msgstr "Film/televidenie shousi kinostudiyalarining logotip tasvirlari uchun Studio Icons plaginini qidiring va agar topilsa, ularni video ko‘rishlarni ko‘rib chiqish vaqtida ko‘rsating."

msgctxt "#31219"
msgid "Search for the album's record label logo using the RecordLabel Icons addon, and if found, display it when browsing the music album views."
msgstr "RecordLabel Icons qo'shimchasidan foydalanib albomning rekord yorlig'i logotipini qidiring va topilsa, musiqa albomi ko'rinishlarini ko'rib chiqayotganda uni ko'rsating."

msgctxt "#31220"
msgid "Show rating"
msgstr "Reytingni ko'rsatish"

msgctxt "#31221"
msgid "Show artist clearart"
msgstr "Rassomning aniq tasvirini ko'rsatish"

msgctxt "#31222"
msgid "Show CD"
msgstr "CDni ko'rsatish"

msgctxt "#31223"
msgid "Show Time"
msgstr "Vaqtni ko'rsatish"

msgctxt "#31224"
msgid "Animated posters"
msgstr "Animatsion plakatlar"

msgctxt "#31225"
msgid "Normal posters"
msgstr "Oddiy plakatlar"

msgctxt "#31226"
msgid "Extra posters"
msgstr "Qo'shimcha plakatlar"

msgctxt "#31227"
msgid "Sets the transparency level of the home menu widgets."
msgstr "Bosh menyu vidjetlarining shaffoflik darajasini belgilaydi."

msgctxt "#31228"
msgid "Displays main menu options in a vertical layout instead of a horizontal one."
msgstr "Asosiy menyu parametrlarini gorizontal emas, balki vertikal tartibda ko'rsatadi."

msgctxt "#31229"
msgid "Set another video file as startup intro"
msgstr "Boshqa video faylni ishga tushirish introsi sifatida o'rnating"

msgctxt "#31230"
msgid "Choose another video file to play when Kodi starts instead of Aeon Tajo default. It's recommended to choose a short one. To stop playback and start using Kodi right away, click or press any arrow key."
msgstr "Standart Aeon Tajo o‘rniga Kodi ishga tushganda ijro etish uchun boshqa video faylni tanlang.Qisqasini tanlash tavsiya etiladi.Ijro etishni to'xtatish va darhol Kodi-dan foydalanishni boshlash uchun istalgan o'q tugmachasini bosing yoki bosing."

msgctxt "#31231"
msgid "Plays an intro video when launching Kodi"
msgstr "Kodi ishga tushirilganda kirish videosini o'ynaydi"

msgctxt "#31232"
msgid "Clear current intro video file and back to default"
msgstr "Joriy kirish video faylini tozalang va standart holatga qayting"

msgctxt "#31233"
msgid "Clear the intro video file selected by the user and back to Aeon Tajo's default."
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi tomonidan tanlangan kirish video faylini tozalang va Aeon Tajo standartiga qayting."

msgctxt "#31234"
msgid "Adds a layer that simulates falling snow on all Kodi screens, with four available intensity levels."
msgstr "Barcha Kodi ekranlarida qor yog‘ayotganini taqlid qiluvchi qatlam qo‘shiladi, to‘rtta intensivlik darajasi mavjud."

msgctxt "#31235"
msgid "Override the current home menu backgrounds with this one"
msgstr "Joriy asosiy menyu fonini shu bilan bekor qiling"

msgctxt "#31236"
msgid "The background selections made in the Setup Main Menu screen will be preserved. Disabling this option will restore all previous backgrounds. This option is particularly designed for use during special seasons."
msgstr "O'rnatishning asosiy menyusi ekranida qilingan fon tanlovlari saqlanib qoladi.Ushbu parametrni o'chirib qo'yish barcha oldingi fonlarni tiklaydi.Ushbu parametr, ayniqsa, maxsus mavsumlarda foydalanish uchun mo'ljallangan."

msgctxt "#31237"
msgid "No impact"
msgstr "Ta'sir yo'q"

msgctxt "#31238"
msgid "Very small"
msgstr "Juda kichik"

msgctxt "#31239"
msgid "Small"
msgstr "Kichik"

msgctxt "#31240"
msgid "Moderate"
msgstr "Oʻrtacha"

msgctxt "#31241"
msgid "Pixel format"
msgstr "Piksel formati"

msgctxt "#31242"
msgid "System rendering speed"
msgstr "Tizimni ko'rsatish tezligi"

msgctxt "#31243"
msgid "Hide actor's thumbnails"
msgstr "Aktyorning eskizlarini berkitish"

msgctxt "#31244"
msgid "Show only a list of the actors' names, instead of also including their thumbnails."
msgstr "Aktyorlarning eskizlarini qo‘shish o‘rniga faqat ismlar ro‘yxatini ko‘rsating."

msgctxt "#31250"
msgid "Automatic Full Screen when playing music"
msgstr "Musiqa tinglashda avtomatik to'liq ekran"

msgctxt "#31251"
msgid "Don't play melodies while in Home Screen"
msgstr "Asosiy ekranda musiqalarni ijro qilmang"

msgctxt "#31252"
msgid "Always show home screen widgets"
msgstr "Har doim asosiy ekran vidjetlarini ko'rsating"

msgctxt "#31253"
msgid "Choose user audio playlist *.m3u (max.10 songs)"
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi audio pleylistini tanlang *.m3u (maksimal 10 ta qo'shiq)"

msgctxt "#31254"
msgid "Clear user playlist (back to default)"
msgstr "Foydalanuvchi pleylistini tozalash (standartga qaytish)"

msgctxt "#31300"
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Umumiy koʻrinish"

msgctxt "#31301"
msgid "Last Updated"
msgstr "Oxirgi yangilangan"

msgctxt "#31307"
msgid "Hide Fanart"
msgstr "Fanartni yashirish"

msgctxt "#31308"
msgid "Next aired"
msgstr "Keyingi efirga uzatildi"

msgctxt "#31309"
msgid "Memory Used:"
msgstr "Ishlatilgan xotira:"

msgctxt "#31310"
msgid "Available audio tracks"
msgstr "Mavjud audio treklar"

msgctxt "#31317"
msgid "Set Fanart Path"
msgstr "Fanart yo'lini o'rnating"

msgctxt "#31320"
msgid "Last Logged In"
msgstr "Oxirgi marta kirgan"

msgctxt "#31321"
msgid "Karaoke Song Selector"
msgstr "Karaoke qo'shiq tanlash"

msgctxt "#31328"
msgid "Recently Added"
msgstr "Yaqinda qo'shilgan"

msgctxt "#31331"
msgid "Installed"
msgstr "Oʻrnatilgan"

msgctxt "#31332"
msgid "Not Installed"
msgstr "Oʻrnatilmagan"

msgctxt "#31334"
msgid "Required"
msgstr "Majburiy"

msgctxt "#31335"
msgid "Recommended"
msgstr "Tavsiya etilgan"

msgctxt "#31336"
msgid "Optional"
msgstr "Ixtiyoriy"

msgctxt "#31390"
msgid "Skin default"
msgstr "Teri standarti"

msgctxt "#31400"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE INTERFACE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change the skin · Set language and region · Setup remote controls[CR]Set up a screensaver · Setup master lock"
msgstr "[B]INTERFEYS SOZLAMALARINI SONLASH[/B][CR][CR]Terni oʻzgartirish · Til va mintaqani sozlash · Masofadan boshqarish vositalarini sozlash[CR]Ekran pardasini oʻrnatish · Asosiy qulfni sozlash"

msgctxt "#31401"
msgid "Menu - press 'OK'"
msgstr "Menyu - "OK" tugmasini bosing"

msgctxt "#31402"
msgid "Enable startup video intro"
msgstr "Boshlanish videosi kirishini yoqing"

msgctxt "#31405"
msgid "[B]MONITOR YOUR SYSTEM[/B][CR][CR]Check out your hardware · Monitor CPU usage[CR]Check Kodi revision number"
msgstr "[B]TIZIMINGIZNI MONITORING[/B][CR][CR]Uskunangizni tekshiring · Protsessordan foydalanishni nazorat qiling[CR]Kodi versiya raqamini tekshiring"

msgctxt "#31406"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SYSTEM SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup and calibrate displays · Configure audio output · [CR]Set power saving options · Enable debugging"
msgstr "[B]TIZIM SOZLAMALARINI SONLASH[/B][CR][CR]Displeylarni sozlash va kalibrlash · Ovoz chiqishini sozlash · [CR]Quvvat tejash parametrlarini sozlash · Nosozliklarni tuzatishni yoqish"

msgctxt "#31407"
msgid "[B]SETUP PROFILES[/B][CR][CR]Setup and manage user profiles · Enable login screen[CR]Change password · Add a profile picture"
msgstr "[B]PROFILLARINI SOZLASH[/B][CR][CR]Foydalanuvchi profillarini sozlash va boshqarish · Kirish ekranini yoqish[CR]Parolni oʻzgartirish · Profil rasmini qoʻshish"

msgctxt "#31409"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE TV SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change full screen info · Manage EPG data settings"
msgstr "[B]TV SOZLAMALARINI SONLASH[/B][CR][CR]Toʻliq ekran maʼlumotlarini oʻzgartirish · EPG maʼlumotlari sozlamalarini boshqarish"

msgctxt "#31410"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SERVICE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup control of Kodi via UPnP and HTTP · Configure file sharing[CR]Enable Zeroconf · Configure AirPlay"
msgstr "[B]XIZMAT SOZLAMALARINI SOZLASH[/B][CR][CR]UPnP va HTTP orqali Kodi boshqaruvini sozlash · Fayl almashishni sozlash[CR]Zeroconfni yoqish · AirPlayni sozlash"

msgctxt "#31412"
msgid "Select section"
msgstr "Bo'limni tanlang"

msgctxt "#31413"
msgid "Local subtitle available"
msgstr "Mahalliy subtitr mavjud"

msgctxt "#31414"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE PLAYER SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Configure video playback · Configure music playback · Configure picture slideshow[CR]Configure video language and subtitles"
msgstr "[B]PLEYER SOZLAMALARINI SOZLASH[/B][CR][CR]Video ijrosini sozlash · Musiqa ijrosini sozlash · Rasmli slayd-shouni sozlash[CR]Video tili va subtitrlarni sozlash"

msgctxt "#31415"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE MEDIA SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Set default select action · Configure file list options · Configure metadata options[CR]Manage databases"
msgstr "[B]MEDIYA SOZLAMALARINI SOZLASH[/B][CR][CR]Birlamchi tanlash amalini oʻrnatish · Fayllar roʻyxati parametrlarini sozlash · Metadata parametrlarini sozlash[CR]Maʼlumotlar bazalarini boshqarish"

msgctxt "#31421"
msgid "Select your Kodi user profile[CR]to login and continue"
msgstr "Kirish va davom etish uchun Kodi foydalanuvchi profilingizni[CR] tanlang"

msgctxt "#31427"
msgid "Skin Shortcuts is responsible for handling all aspects of the main menu."
msgstr "Skin Shortcuts asosiy menyuning barcha jihatlarini boshqarish uchun javobgardir."

msgctxt "#31428"
msgid "The Grab Fanart script provides the random fanart slideshows for the main menu."
msgstr "Grab Fanart skripti asosiy menyu uchun tasodifiy fanart slayd-shoularini taqdim etadi."

msgctxt "#31429"
msgid "Library Data Provider is a service that runs in the background to provide library data for widgets and live backgrounds as well as playlist statistics for infolines."
msgstr "Kutubxona maʼlumotlari provayderi vidjetlar va jonli fonlar uchun kutubxona maʼlumotlarini hamda maʼlumot qatorlari uchun pleylist statistikasini taqdim etish uchun fonda ishlaydigan xizmatdir."

msgctxt "#31430"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white studio icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Teri bo'ylab standart oq studiya piktogrammalarini ko'rsatish uchun resurs tasviri qo'shimchasi."

msgctxt "#31431"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white recording label icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Teri bo'ylab standart oq yozuv yorlig'i piktogrammalarini ko'rsatish uchun manba tasviri qo'shimchasi."

msgctxt "#31432"
msgid "Provides numerous Widget options and extended cast and crew metadata."
msgstr "Ko'p sonli Vidjet variantlari va kengaytirilgan aktyorlar va ekipaj metama'lumotlarini taqdim etadi."

msgctxt "#31433"
msgid "Skin Info Service is used to display movie set information throughout the skin."
msgstr "Skin Info Service butun teri bo'ylab filmlar to'plami ma'lumotlarini ko'rsatish uchun ishlatiladi."

msgctxt "#31434"
msgid "Check MP3 Theme checks whether the user has put a theme.mp3 file in the corresponding movie/TV show folder to be played when browsing."
msgstr "Tekshirish MP3 Theme foydalanuvchi theme.mp3 faylni koʻrish vaqtida oʻynaladigan tegishli film/TV shou papkasiga qoʻyganligini tekshiradi."

msgctxt "#31450"
msgid "  •  Open Settings "
msgstr "• Sozlamalarni oching"

msgctxt "#31451"
msgid "  •  Click to Install"
msgstr "• O‘rnatish uchun bosing"

msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Aeon Tajo Helper provides the data to display the cast for movies and TV shows."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo Helper filmlar va teleko'rsatuvlar uchun kadrlarni ko'rsatish uchun ma'lumotlarni taqdim etadi."

msgctxt "#31474"
msgid "CU LRC Lyrics is used to download, sync, and display lyrics during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "CU LRC Lyrics musiqani toʻliq ekranda ijro etish vaqtida matnlarni yuklab olish, sinxronlash va koʻrsatish uchun ishlatiladi."

msgctxt "#31475"
msgid "Play Trailer makes possible to play movie trailers through a context menu. "
msgstr "Play Trailer kontekst menyusi orqali film treylerini ijro etish imkonini beradi."

msgctxt "#31476"
msgid "Allows the use of Youtube to play trailers and other videos."
msgstr "Treylerlar va boshqa videolarni ijro etish uchun Youtube-dan foydalanishga ruxsat beradi."

msgctxt "#31477"
msgid "Provides some cast actress images to be shown in video views."
msgstr "Video ko‘rinishlarida ko‘rsatiladigan aktyorlar suratlarini taqdim etadi."

msgctxt "#31478"
msgid "Artist Slideshow is used to display artist fanart for both the home screen and during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Ijrochining slayd-shousi ham bosh ekranda, ham musiqani toʻliq ekranda ijro etishda rassom fanartini koʻrsatish uchun ishlatiladi."

msgctxt "#31479"
msgid "AutoCompletion provides suggestions to be selected while using the virtual keyboard."
msgstr "Avtomatik yakunlash virtual klaviaturadan foydalanishda tanlash uchun takliflar beradi."

msgctxt "#31480"
msgid "Library Editor Script uses JSON to directly edit your database information."
msgstr "Kutubxona muharriri skripti ma'lumotlar bazasi ma'lumotlarini to'g'ridan-to'g'ri tahrirlash uchun JSON-dan foydalanadi."

msgctxt "#31481"
msgid "Global Search makes possible to search among all the items (movies, TV shows, music, actors, etc.) in your collection."
msgstr "Global Qidiruv kollektsiyangizdagi barcha narsalarni (filmlar, teleko'rsatuvlar, musiqa, aktyorlar va h.k.) qidirish imkonini beradi."

msgctxt "#31501"
msgid "Channel group"
msgstr "Kanal guruhi"

msgctxt "#31502"
msgid "Live TV"
msgstr "Jonli TV"

msgctxt "#31503"
msgid "Add Group"
msgstr "Guruh qo'shish"

msgctxt "#31504"
msgid "Rename Group"
msgstr "Guruh nomini o'zgartirish"

msgctxt "#31505"
msgid "Delete Group"
msgstr "Guruhni o'chirish"

msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Available[CR]Groups"
msgstr "Mavjud[CR]Guruhlar"

msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Channel Options"
msgstr "Kanal parametrlari"

msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "Show similar movies in Shelf 3D view"
msgstr "Shu kabi filmlarni Shelf 3D ko‘rinishida ko‘rsatish"

msgctxt "#31901"
msgid "36 Hour Forecast"
msgstr "36 soatlik prognoz"

msgctxt "#31902"
msgid "Hourly Forecast"
msgstr "Soatlik prognoz"

msgctxt "#31903"
msgid "Weekend Forecast"
msgstr "Dam olish kunlari prognozi"

msgctxt "#31904"
msgid "10 Day Forecast"
msgstr "10 kunlik prognoz"

msgctxt "#31908"
msgid "Chance of Precipitation"
msgstr "Yog'ingarchilik ehtimoli"

msgctxt "#31909"
msgid "Fetching forecast info..."
msgstr "Prognoz maʼlumotlari olinmoqda..."

msgctxt "#31910"
msgid "Map & Alerts"
msgstr "Xarita va ogohlantirishlar"

msgctxt "#31911"
msgid "Setup the Aeon Tajo main menu"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo asosiy menyusini sozlang"

msgctxt "#31912"
msgid "Customize the main menu with widgets, backgrounds and statistics. Add your own custom main menu items."
msgstr "Asosiy menyuni vidjetlar, fon va statistika bilan moslashtiring.Shaxsiy asosiy menyu elementlarini qo'shing."

msgctxt "#31913"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu vertical position"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo asosiy menyusi vertikal holati"

msgctxt "#31914"
msgid "Change the vertical position of the main menu. Default is centered on screen."
msgstr "Asosiy menyuning vertikal holatini o'zgartiring.Standart ekranda markazlashtirilgan."

msgctxt "#31915"
msgid "Navigation style for horizontal lists"
msgstr "Gorizontal ro'yxatlar uchun navigatsiya uslubi"

msgctxt "#31916"
msgid "Change the way horizontal lists scroll in Aeon Tajo. Default will scroll lists in a cycle. \"Fixed\" are lists with a beginning and end."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo'da gorizontal ro'yxatlarni aylantirish usulini o'zgartiring.Standart roʻyxatlarni tsiklda aylantiradi.\"Fixed\" - boshi va oxiri bo'lgan ro'yxatlar."

msgctxt "#31917"
msgid "When enabled text scrolls automatically. When disabled manual scrolling is required. Note that most textboxes don't have a manual button."
msgstr "Yoqilganda matn avtomatik ravishda aylanadi.O'chirilganda qo'lda aylantirish kerak.Ko'pgina matn qutilarida qo'lda tugma mavjud emasligini unutmang."

msgctxt "#31918"
msgid "Projects the current playing video on the background behind the panels."
msgstr "Joriy ijro etilayotgan videoni panellar orqasidagi fonda loyihalashtiradi."

msgctxt "#31919"
msgid "Projects the visualisation on the background behind the panels when music is played."
msgstr "Musiqa ijro etilganda vizualizatsiyani panellar orqasidagi fonda aks ettiradi."

msgctxt "#31920"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when music is playing."
msgstr "Musiqa ijro etilayotganda media ma'lumotlari bilan vidjetni asosiy ekranda ko'rsatadi."

msgctxt "#31921"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when a movie or episode is playing."
msgstr "Film yoki epizod ijro etilayotganda media ma’lumotlari bilan vidjetni asosiy ekranda ko‘rsatadi."

msgctxt "#31922"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the videolibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Bu videokutubxonaning janr tugunini koʻrib chiqishda maxsus janr fonlarini yoqish imkonini beradi.Fayl nomlari janr yorlig'iga mos kelishi kerak.Kengaytma .jpg bo'lishi kerak."

msgctxt "#31923"
msgid "Set a default select action to enable this item."
msgstr "Ushbu elementni yoqish uchun standart tanlash amalini o'rnating."

msgctxt "#31924"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the musiclibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Bu musiqa kutubxonasining janr tugunini ko'rib chiqishda maxsus janr fonlarini yoqish imkonini beradi.Fayl nomlari janr yorlig'iga mos kelishi kerak.Kengaytma .jpg bo'lishi kerak."

msgctxt "#31925"
msgid "Pick one of the preset backgrounds or set your own images as the menu items background."
msgstr "Oldindan o'rnatilgan fonlardan birini tanlang yoki menyu elementlari foni sifatida o'zingizning rasmlaringizni o'rnating."

msgctxt "#31926"
msgid "Select add-ons, playlists or favourites. Choose 'Custom' for any of Kodi's built-in functions. (http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"
msgstr "Qo'shimchalar, pleylistlar yoki sevimlilarni tanlang.Kodi-ning o'rnatilgan har qanday funksiyasi uchun "Maxsus" ni tanlang.(http://kodi.wiki/?title=O'rnatilgan_funktsiyalar_ro'yxati)"

msgctxt "#31927"
msgid "Resets all above values to their defaults."
msgstr "Yuqoridagi barcha qiymatlarni asl holatiga qaytaradi."

msgctxt "#31928"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu layout"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo asosiy menyu tartibi"

msgctxt "#31929"
msgid "This setting defines how much items will be visible on the main menu. Options are 3 items or 5 items."
msgstr "Ushbu parametr asosiy menyuda qancha elementlar ko'rinishini belgilaydi.Variantlar 3 ta yoki 5 ta elementdan iborat."

msgctxt "#31930"
msgid "Choose a widget to display on the Home screen to have easy access to content from the library."
msgstr "Kutubxonadagi kontentga oson kirish uchun asosiy ekranda ko‘rsatish uchun vidjetni tanlang."

msgctxt "#31931"
msgid "Video plot preference"
msgstr "Video syujet afzalligi"

msgctxt "#31932"
msgid "Show plot outline in the library views and full plot in the video information dialog or vice versa. Falls back to full plot if no outline is available."
msgstr "Kutubxona ko‘rinishlarida syujet konturini va videoma’lumot muloqot oynasida to‘liq syujetni ko‘rsating yoki aksincha.Agar kontur mavjud bo'lmasa, to'liq syujetga qaytadi."

msgctxt "#31933"
msgid "Select an item to display on the left top of the main menu"
msgstr "Asosiy menyuning yuqori chap qismida ko'rsatiladigan elementni tanlang"

msgctxt "#31935"
msgid "Switch places with another menu item. Opens a dialog with a list of menu items to choose from."
msgstr "Boshqa menyu elementi bilan joylarni almashtiring.Tanlash uchun menyu elementlari ro'yxati bilan dialog oynasini ochadi."

msgctxt "#31937"
msgid "Show the RSS feed on the bottom or top of the screen, depending on main menu position. Enabling this setting makes the submenu permanently visible."
msgstr "Asosiy menyu holatiga qarab, ekranning pastki yoki yuqori qismida RSS tasmasi ko'rsating.Ushbu sozlamani yoqsangiz, pastki menyu doimiy ko'rinadigan bo'ladi."

msgctxt "#31938"
msgid "Enables extra information in the TV show library, like TV show status, next / latest episode, etc. Depends on TV Show Next Aired add-on."
msgstr "Teleko‘rsatuvlar kutubxonasida teleshou holati, keyingi/oxirgi epizod va h.k. kabi qo‘shimcha ma’lumotlarni yoqadi. Teleko‘rsatuv Keyingi efirga uzatilgan qo‘shimchasiga bog‘liq."

msgctxt "#31939"
msgid "Hide Infopanel on scrolling"
msgstr "O'tkazishda Infopanelni yashirish"

msgctxt "#31940"
msgid "Hides the infopanel for Showcase and Landscape view (if activated) while scrolling through the library. Set the amount of seconds to wait for the infopanel to appear when scrolling is stopped."
msgstr "Kutubxona boʻylab aylanayotganda Vitrin va Landshaft koʻrinishi (agar faollashtirilgan boʻlsa) uchun maʼlumot panelini yashiradi.O'tkazish to'xtatilganda ma'lumot paneli paydo bo'lishini kutish uchun soniyalar miqdorini belgilang."

msgctxt "#31941"
msgid "Kiosk mode"
msgstr "Kiosk rejimi"

msgctxt "#31942"
msgid "Disables the slide out menu (media menu) in the library as well as certain buttons in the media information dialogs. (Requires restart to take effect)"
msgstr "Kutubxonadagi slaydni chiqarish menyusini (media menyusi), shuningdek, media ma'lumotlari dialog oynalaridagi ba'zi tugmalarni o'chiradi.(Kuchga kirishi uchun qayta ishga tushirish talab qilinadi)"

msgctxt "#31943"
msgid "Watched status indicator"
