msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Aeon Tajo-dan foydalanganingiz uchun tashakkur - bu sizga yoqadi degan umiddaman.Bunday Kodi terisini yaratish va unga xizmat ko'rsatish yuzlab soatlik mehnatni talab qiladi.Agar Aeon Tajo sizga yoqadigan va foydali deb topadigan narsa bo'lsa, uni qo'llab-quvvatlash menga u ustida ishlashni davom ettirishga yordam beradi va kelajakda rivojlanishda davom etishini ta'minlaydi.[CR][CR]Agar shunday qilishga qaror qilsangiz, sizga tez-tez yangi funksiyalar va xatoliklar tuzatilgan yangilanishlar, shuningdek, videolar, media toʻplamlar va kuzatib borish oson maqolalar, Aeon Tajo taqdim etayotgan barcha imkoniyatlardan maksimal darajada foydalanishga yordam beradigan batafsil maslahatlar hamda qoʻllab-quvvatlaganingiz uchun samimiy minnatdorchilik bildiraman.[CR][CR]Batafsil maʼlumot uchun [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] sahifasiga tashrif buyuring va ijodkorni qidiring [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR] yoki [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo][B]patreon.com/aeontajo][OR!]T. sahifasiga oʻting."

